    "name": "佩奇卡",
    "steam_appid": 2210700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/39872e557467e2822b1f251f8338e4ee.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>20世纪初，一个消失的国家的市民们开始了战斗。而在其中心，是年轻人&quot;彼得&quot;，他没有选择任何国家。<br><br>体验一部以真实历史为背景的故事，成为自己的主角！您可以在悲惨战争的历史中体验一个悲伤的故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引人入胜的故事</strong></h2>《佩奇卡》是以年轻人“彼得”的旅程为中心，以消失的国家公民的斗争和冲突为核心的故事。请沉浸在在战争的悲惨历史中展开的戏剧中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经过严谨验证的历史事实和可靠资料来源</strong></h2>从第一次世界大战到布尔什维克革命再到韩国的独立运动，本游戏设定在20世纪初的俄罗斯远东，通过提供详尽的历史和时代真实性，为玩家提供真实的体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/394a80b45aecbeea40288f1bec9441f8.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/394a80b45aecbeea40288f1bec9441f8.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/394a80b45aecbeea40288f1bec9441f8.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>背叛、死亡与爱</strong></h2>《佩奇卡》探索了背叛、死亡和爱情等多种情感和主题。通过这些，玩家将与角色的选择和困惑共情，体验到各种情感的流露。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亲密度系统和多个结局</strong></h2>留意与角色之间的亲密度，它会根据玩家的选择和行动而改变。这些互动将导致不同的结局。通过您自己的选择发现这个时代悲剧的影响。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/aaf0faec57682cff58c25ef648498468.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/aaf0faec57682cff58c25ef648498468.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/aaf0faec57682cff58c25ef648498468.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小故事</strong></h2>游戏通过揭示小故事的方式推进，贡献于整体叙事的完成。玩家通过探索和在这些故事中作出选择，沉浸在这个动荡的时代中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可爱的猫咪们</strong></h2>游戏中有许多可爱的猫咪出现，为游戏世界增添了愉悦的氛围。<br>请在游戏的各个地方发现这些不同的猫咪。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
